1
00:00:01,296 --> 00:00:02,529
My name is Oliver Queen.

2
00:00:03,368 --> 00:00:04,665
After 5 years in Hell,

3
00:00:04,666 --> 00:00:06,772
I returned home
with only one goal--

4
00:00:06,872 --> 00:00:08,505
to save my city.

5
00:00:08,507 --> 00:00:10,908
Today, I fight that war
on two fronts.

6
00:00:10,910 --> 00:00:13,277
By day, I lead Star City
as its mayor,

7
00:00:13,279 --> 00:00:15,446
but by night,
I am someone else.

8
00:00:15,448 --> 00:00:17,715
I am...Something else.

9
00:00:17,717 --> 00:00:20,384
I am the Green Arrow.

10
00:00:20,386 --> 00:00:22,052
Previously on "Arrow"...

11
00:00:22,054 --> 00:00:23,053
You want to help?

12
00:00:23,055 --> 00:00:24,054
Yeah.

13
00:00:24,056 --> 00:00:25,289
Stay off the streets.

14
00:00:25,291 --> 00:00:26,624
<b><font color="#FF8000">Rene:</font></b> It's my city, too.

15
00:00:26,626 --> 00:00:27,858
I came here to work
with the guy

16
00:00:27,860 --> 00:00:29,026
who killed Damien Darhk.

17
00:00:29,028 --> 00:00:30,628
So you're ex-Navy, right?

18
00:00:30,630 --> 00:00:31,662
Dishonorably discharged.

19
00:00:31,664 --> 00:00:32,896
Reason?

20
00:00:32,898 --> 00:00:34,298
Because I screwed up...

21
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:36,166
Again.

22
00:00:36,168 --> 00:00:38,369
That's my life, man.

23
00:00:38,371 --> 00:00:39,803
I'm wearing this suit again

24
00:00:39,805 --> 00:00:41,138
because I think it's
a path to redemption,

25
00:00:41,140 --> 00:00:42,640
and it could be
for you, too.

26
00:00:42,642 --> 00:00:44,308
<b><font color="#FF8000">Oliver:</font></b> But finding
a new Black Canary

27
00:00:44,310 --> 00:00:46,210
isn't just about
reviewing resumes.

28
00:00:46,212 --> 00:00:48,612
<b><font color="#FF8000">Curtis:</font></b> Tina Boland,
formerly of the CCPD.

29
00:00:48,614 --> 00:00:51,649
She's a kick-ass woman who appears
out of nowhere and saves crime victims.

30
00:00:51,651 --> 00:00:53,250
She even has a cry.

31
00:00:53,252 --> 00:00:55,886
<font color="#0CEC0C">[Canary cry]</font>

32
00:00:55,888 --> 00:00:58,322
<b><font color="#FF8000">Oliver:</font></b> Our Tina is trying
to avenge her former partner.

33
00:00:58,324 --> 00:01:00,124
Please!

34
00:01:00,126 --> 00:01:01,992
How do you keep living
with so much pain?

35
00:01:01,994 --> 00:01:03,994
I can tell you it helps
to not be alone.

36
00:01:03,996 --> 00:01:05,329
My real name is Dinah--

37
00:01:05,331 --> 00:01:07,297
Dinah Drake.

38
00:01:26,308 --> 00:01:30,308
<b><font color="#00FF00">♪ Arrow 5x13 ♪</font></b>
